On the 23rd anniversary of Kargil Vijay Diwas, we remember the brave soldiers who fought valiantly and sacrificed their lives to secure victory for our great nation in the Kargil War. #JawaYezdiMotorcycles salutes our #ForeverHeroes and their gallant efforts on the battlefield.
Jai Hind!

#KargilVijayDiwas2022 #23YearsofKargil #KargilWar #JawaMotorcycles #YezdiForever #KargilHeroes #IndianArmy

Some bonds, once formed, last forever. It’s an indelible connection shared by countless #JawaYezdi owners old and new with their motorcycles – and within the #Kommuniti that they form! It’s a family created out of a shared passion, and the unforgettable experiences they bring. 
.
This year’s International Jawa Yezdi Day celebration in Bangalore was a lively example of these bonds in action, as scores of passionate motorcycle owners came together to celebrate their shared love for Jawa and Yezdi motorcycles. Watch now!
.
#JawaYezdiDay22 #IJYD2022 #Jawa #JawaMotorcycles #JawaYezdiMotorcycles #Yezdi #YezdiForever

Journey to the mystical lands of the North East alongside the Jawa Yezdi Nomads, as they explore its lush green valleys, navigate through its winding trails and live through the fascinating stories it offers!
.
The Taktsang Trail 2022 saw 14 Jawa Yezdi Nomads cover over 1000kms across the breathtaking lands of Assam, Arunachal Pradesh and Nagaland. Come witness the pristine land unfold its true flavors as the Nomads soak in the rich and vibrant culture of the storied North-East. 

#Jawa #JawaMotorcycles #Yezdi #YezdiForever #JawaYezdiMotorcycles #TaktsangTrail #NorthEast #JawaYezdiNomads #Assam #ArunachalPradesh #Nagaland

In the rain-soaked month of May, 14 members of the Jawa Yezdi Nomads went exploring the lush green lands of the North-east. They were greeted by winding trails, thrilling terrains & fascinating stories! Want to see more? Stay tuned.

#Jawa #JawaMotorcycles #Yezdi #YezdiForever #JawaYezdiMotorcycles #TaktsangTrail #NorthEast #JawaYezdiNomads #Assam #ArunachalPradesh #Nagaland

Only a true motorcyclist knows how special Jawa & Yezdi motorcycles are. These are the machines that make you fall in love with the art of motorcycling & reignite the lost love for raw motorcycling.
.
See how the Yezdi CL2 made Srinivas from @roaringridersclub fall in love with the art of motorcycling back in his childhood days & how the Jawa Perak reignited the same love & passion for motorcycling at the launch event. Follow his journey as he opens up about his love affair with the Jawa & Yezdi motorcycles.

#NotForTheSaintHearted #Yezdi #YezdiForever #YezdiIsBack #JawaYezdiMotorcycles #JawaMotorcycles #Jawa #Biker #Motorcycle #IJYD2022 #JawaYezdiDay

There's always been a unique bond between music and motorcycling. Don’t we always have that one track playing in our heads as we ride? 
.
This World Motorcycle & Music Day, we take a look back at the time when Jawa Yezdi Motorcycles rode to Ladakh to celebrate the first ever #LadakhInternationalMusicFestival 
.
Music. Mountains. Magic. Could we ask for more? What’re your plans today?
